      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Crack/fracture · Fatigue · Wear/rubbing\nCorrosion/pitting · FOD · Creep · Erosion\nBearing fault · Overheating · …\nflat list, lives in Python, applied in the\nwrite path; unknown mechanisms pass\nthrough as free text; no hierarchy —\nLCF/HCF/fretting all collapse to 'Fatigue'",
      "fontSize": 10.5,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Crack/fracture · Fatigue · Wear/rubbing\nCorrosion/pitting · FOD · Creep · Erosion\nBearing fault · Overheating · …\nflat list, lives in Python, applied in the\nwrite path; unknown mechanisms pass\nthrough as free text; no hierarchy —\nLCF/HCF/fretting all collapse to 'Fatigue'",
