      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. pending_classification: the paper was found by\nthe discovery sweep but hasn't been processed\nby the LLM\n2. classified: the paper was classified by the\nLLM\n3. stale: the paper hasn't appeared in the\ndiscovery sweep in 60 days\n4. removed: the paper hasn't appeared in the\ndiscovery sweep in 180 days",
