      "originalText": "1. pending_classification: the paper was found by the discovery sweep but hasn't been processed by the LLM\n2. classified: the paper was classified by the LLM\n3. stale: the paper hasn't appeared in the discovery sweep in 60 days\n4. removed: the paper hasn't appeared in the discovery sweep in 180 days",
